<p>In Las Cruces, NM Alma d’arte Charter High School exists as a public high school that is open to any high school student living in Las Cruces.</p>
<p>Students enrolled at this school DO NOT pay any tuition or other fees to attend classes.  Certain eligibility requirements regarding academic achievement must be met.</p>
<p>Since 2004  Alma d’ arte has been serving students and families who want a choice when it comes to education, we assure you that our mission and vision is strong.</p>
<hr>
<h3>Principal/CAO Dr. Dan Lere</h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-5274 size-large" src="https://www.almadarte.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/almadarte-art-school-4-1030x343.jpg" alt="" width="1030" height="343" srcset="https://www.almadarte.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/almadarte-art-school-4-1030x343.jpg 1030w, https://www.almadarte.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/almadarte-art-school-4-300x100.jpg 300w, https://www.almadarte.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/almadarte-art-school-4-768x256.jpg 768w, https://www.almadarte.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/almadarte-art-school-4.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1030px) 100vw, 1030px"></p>
<p>Our principal, Dan Lere, is working diligently to ensure that Alma continues to succeed academically and artistically. A new year means new beginnings and celebrations. Alma d’arte Charter High School at the Court Youth Center is the pioneering arts-based secondary school serving a diversity of learners through a rigorous academic and integrated arts program since 2004.</p>
<p> </p>
<hr>
<p> </p>
<h2>Alma’s dynamic educational program</h2>
<p>Alma’s educational program integrates the visual, performing, literary, media, and culinary arts into academic content areas. Students learn to understand and creatively explore the connections between disciplines and diverse ways of thinking.</p>
<p>This integrated approach ensures that students develop into creative thinkers equipped to better succeed in a complex society where personal, professional and artistic boundaries are increasingly fluid and career multi-faceted.</p>
<hr>
