<p> </p>
<p><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Alma d’arte search for new Principal/CAO for the 20-21 school year</span></p>
<p>The search has begun for a new Principal/CAO for the upcoming school year. Interested applicants may click the link for information!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.almadarte.org/principal-cao-job-posting/">Principal CAO job posting</a></p>
